# Database Models

## Key Models

```prisma
model Tenant {
  id          String   @id @default(cuid())
  name        String
  slug        String   @unique
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt
}
```

Every tenant-owned model should include:

```prisma
tenantId String
tenant   Tenant @relation(fields: [tenantId], references: [id])
```

# Inventory Features

## Inventory Items

- SKU
- Name
- Description
- Category
- Unit of measure
- Reorder point
- Current stock
- Warehouse location
- Barcode
- Status

## Stock Tracking

- Quantity on hand
- Quantity reserved
- Quantity available
- Quantity incoming
- Stock adjustments
- Movement history

Formula:

```ts
available = onHand - reserved
```

# Forms and Validation

Use:

- React Hook Form
- Zod
- @hookform/resolvers
- Shadcn form components

Example:

```ts
import { z } from "zod";

export const inventoryItemSchema = z.object({
  sku: z.string().min(1),
  name: z.string().min(1),
  description: z.string().optional(),
  reorderPoint: z.coerce.number().min(0),
});
```

