# Claude Instructions

1. Use server components by default.
2. Scope every query by tenantId.
3. Never expose tenant data across tenants.
4. Use Zod validation everywhere.
5. Use React Hook Form with zodResolver.
6. Use Shadcn UI components.
7. Prefer server actions.
8. Add authorization checks to every mutation.

